{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"16a69de318","title":"对新华社的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba2dc31ce4","index":0,"year":1964,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"16a69de318"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5030dbcf50","type":"paragraph","text":"谈到人民日报上“桌子的哲学”的讨论，主席说：观念是从实践来的。人们从土堆，石堆，或者别的东西中，逐渐有了桌子的想法。做桌子，把想法提高了一步，是一个飞跃。而做出来的桌子同原来想法已经不同，又进了一步，这又是一个飞跃。王若水同志可以写篇东西来补正一下。C","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"16a69de318"},{"id":"a756206492","type":"paragraph","text":"×××谈到这个讨论时说：如象有的文章说的，人造的东西都是先有观念，这不对，这就成了唯心主义了。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"16a69de318"},{"id":"5ba5513ee9","type":"paragraph","text":"××说，报低要把两方面的意见都登出来。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"16a69de318"},{"id":"a371dbf119","type":"paragraph","text":"（据×××说：报纸理论版近来登了些讨论，但主席还没有形成已经有改进的印象。因此康生同志提出，决定在学术版挂起“学术研究”的牌子，并准备一周出两次。）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"16a69de318"},{"id":"a8a44acbda","type":"paragraph","text":"对新华社的指示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"16a69de318"},{"id":"e1a45e83fa","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年春）你们新华社只有几千人